Create a .env file in root folder of this app
Copy one of the below envs to the .env to run the app

For Dev environments:
SERVER_PORT=8080

REDIS_ADDR=localhost:6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=nil
REDIS_DB=0

ARGON_2_TIME=1
ARGON_2_MEMORY=65536
ARGON_2_THREADS=4
ARGON_2_KEY_LENGTH=32

JWT_SECRET_KEY=f2@$%&dfdf5%&*@fk4%2*&

For Prod environments (set the values of your choice before deployment):
SERVER_PORT=8080

REDIS_ADDR=redis:6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=nil
REDIS_DB=0

ARGON_2_TIME=1
ARGON_2_MEMORY=65536
ARGON_2_THREADS=4
ARGON_2_KEY_LENGTH=32

JWT_SECRET_KEY=f2@$%&dfdf5%&*@fk4%2*&